        "# Tiempo esperado de absorción\n",
        "\n",
        "El vector de tiempos esperados se calcula mediante:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "t = F\\mathbf{1}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "donde:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\mathbf{1} =\n",
        "\\begin{pmatrix}\n",
        "1 \\\\\n",
        "1 \\\\\n",
        "\\vdots \\\\\n",
        "1\n",
        "\\end{pmatrix}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "Cada entrada \\(t_i\\) representa el número esperado de tiradas para llegar a la casilla final iniciando desde el estado \\(i\\)."
      ],
